name: ClickCells: Office Lady
description:
What does a girl do when she is left alone? You can find out if you go through ClickCells to the end!
In the game you have to solve puzzles with multi-colored cubes. Your task is to destroy all the orange cubes, and deliver the blue to the platform, and in between the levels enjoy the images of a beautiful naked girl.
